      "layout": "The page primarily uses a full-bleed layout, allowing background visuals to extend to the viewport edges. The hero section features a large, ornate display headline centered over the abstract 3D background. Content sections follow a consistent vertical rhythm with minimal visual dividers, flowing seamlessly. Navigation is a compact, right-aligned bar. Text is predominantly left-aligned, creating clear reading paths within the spacious design.",
